[{"data":1,"prerenderedAt":296},["ShallowReactive",2],{"header-locale:\u002Fnodejs\u002F20190626\u002F1885201810\u002F":3,"page:\u002Fnodejs\u002F20190626\u002F1885201810\u002F":4,"alt:\u002Fnodejs\u002F20190626\u002F1885201810\u002F":3,"prev-next:\u002Fnodejs\u002F20190626\u002F1885201810\u002F":272,"related:\u002Fnodejs\u002F20190626\u002F1885201810\u002F":281},"\u002Fen\u002Fnodejs\u002F2019\u002F06\u002F26\u002Fnodejs-basics-install-and-hello-world\u002F",{"id":5,"title":6,"abbrlink":7,"altUrl":3,"body":8,"category":256,"date":257,"description":18,"extension":258,"lang":259,"meta":260,"navigation":261,"path":262,"readingMinutes":263,"seo":264,"standalone":265,"stem":266,"tags":267,"tldr":269,"updated":269,"url":270,"__hash__":271},"content\u002F全端勇士之路 Node.js\u002F全端勇士之路-Node-js-基礎學習-基礎篇.md","全端勇士之路 Node.js 基礎學習-基礎篇","1885201810",{"type":9,"value":10,"toc":244},"minimark",[11,15,19,23,31,34,37,42,45,52,55,58,68,72,75,94,97,100,103,116,119,122,128,131,134,151,154,163,166,172,175,179,182,188,194,199,206,211,218,223,226,229,237,240],[12,13,14],"h2",{"id":14},"前言",[16,17,18],"p",{},"又是一篇基礎學習系列的開啟，這是為了讓自己對 Node.js 觀念及開發更清楚所撰寫的系列文章，廢話不多說就開始吧~",[12,20,22],{"id":21},"nodejs","Node.js",[16,24,25,26,30],{},"首先在學習任何一個新事物的時候，都要先做好一件事情也就是",[27,28,29],"strong",{},"科普","。",[16,32,33],{},"不論我們在選擇寫任何語言的時候，通常我們都會去查這個程式語言可以做哪些事情、未來的發展又如何等等，在這邊也不另外。",[16,35,36],{},"以往我們前端工程師與後端工程師所學習的程式語言是不一樣的，以前端工程師來講，主要的程式語言技能術就是 JavaScript、CSS、HTML，而後端可能就有許多選擇 C#、PHP、Python 等等語言，至從出現 Node.js 之後，前端工程師也可以接觸到後端，而撰寫的程式碼也主要使用 JavaScript!",[38,39,41],"h3",{"id":40},"v8-引擎","V8 引擎",[16,43,44],{},"Node.js 主要所使用的是由 Google 所推出的 v8 引擎",[16,46,47],{},[48,49],"img",{"alt":50,"src":51},"Google v8 引擎","https:\u002F\u002Fi.imgur.com\u002Fqt9kuez.png",[16,53,54],{},"而 v8 引擎是做什麼用的呢?簡單來講就是透過這個引擎將 JavaScript 轉換為電腦可以懂得指令，而 Google Chrome 就搭載這個引擎。",[16,56,57],{},"當然每一間的瀏覽器引擎是不相同的，以 Firefox 來講則是 Gecko、SpiderMonkey 這兩種，但是這邊就不多介紹，因為這邊主要是要講 Node.js",[16,59,60,61],{},"有興趣可以參考這篇文章 ",[62,63,67],"a",{"href":64,"rel":65},"https:\u002F\u002Fzh.wikipedia.org\u002Fwiki\u002FJavaScript%E5%BC%95%E6%93%8E",[66],"nofollow","Wiki",[38,69,71],{"id":70},"nodejs-優勢","Node.js 優勢",[16,73,74],{},"然而 Node.js 有哪些優勢呢?",[76,77,78,82,85,88,91],"ul",{},[79,80,81],"li",{},"開源",[79,83,84],{},"v8 引擎",[79,86,87],{},"可以脫離 Apache HTTP Server 或 IIS，作為獨立伺服器執行",[79,89,90],{},"框架多 - Express.js、Socket.IO、Connect 以及較新的 Koa.js",[79,92,93],{},"可以使用替代語言開發 (CoffeeScript、TypeScript、Dart 等語言)",[16,95,96],{},"講了那麼多，就先來準備一些環境設置吧",[12,98,99],{"id":99},"環境設置篇",[16,101,102],{},"首先要先到官方網站安裝 Node.js",[16,104,105,106,111],{},"官方網站:\n",[62,107,110],{"href":108,"rel":109},"https:\u002F\u002Fnodejs.org\u002Fzh-tw\u002F",[66],"中文官網",[62,112,115],{"href":113,"rel":114},"https:\u002F\u002Fnodejs.org\u002Fen\u002F",[66],"英文官網",[16,117,118],{},"兩者擇一進入官網下載即可。",[16,120,121],{},"接下來建議選擇 LTS 版本(也就是長期維護版)，如果選擇 Current (先行版)，有可能會出現某些套件不支援的狀況。",[16,123,124],{},[48,125],{"alt":126,"src":127},"安裝 LTS 版本(也就是長期維護版)","https:\u002F\u002Fi.imgur.com\u002F67U49JW.png",[16,129,130],{},"安裝過程就快速忽略，反正只是下一步下一步而已...",[16,132,133],{},"接下來如何確定自己已經安裝成功呢?打開 CMD 輸入以下指令",[135,136,141],"pre",{"className":137,"code":138,"language":139,"meta":140,"style":140},"language-cmd shiki shiki-themes github-dark-high-contrast","node -v\n","cmd","",[142,143,144],"code",{"__ignoreMap":140},[145,146,149],"span",{"class":147,"line":148},"line",1,[145,150,138],{},[16,152,153],{},"or",[135,155,157],{"className":137,"code":156,"language":139,"meta":140,"style":140},"node -version\n",[142,158,159],{"__ignoreMap":140},[145,160,161],{"class":147,"line":148},[145,162,156],{},[16,164,165],{},"當你有看到版本號的時候，就代表你安裝成功哩\n(我習慣使用 PowerShell，只是介面不同而已，指令都一樣)",[16,167,168],{},[48,169],{"alt":170,"src":171},"node -v","https:\u002F\u002Fi.imgur.com\u002FIx4bbjl.png",[16,173,174],{},"(當初因為一些專案開發上的需求，所以我是裝 Current，但建議還是安裝 LTS 會比較好唷)",[12,176,178],{"id":177},"hello-world","Hello World",[16,180,181],{},"接下來我們在桌面上建立一個 project 資料夾，並在底下建立一個 all.js",[16,183,184],{},[48,185],{"alt":186,"src":187},"建立一個 all.js","https:\u002F\u002Fi.imgur.com\u002Fp9lFFbl.png",[16,189,190,191],{},"all.js 裡面輸入 ",[142,192,193],{},"console.log('Hello World');",[16,195,196],{},[48,197],{"alt":178,"src":198},"https:\u002F\u002Fi.imgur.com\u002FPtT8B2l.png",[16,200,201,202,205],{},"接下來打開終端機 ",[142,203,204],{},"cd"," 進入專案目錄",[16,207,208],{},[48,209],{"alt":204,"src":210},"https:\u002F\u002Fi.imgur.com\u002FKR0hDKE.png",[16,212,213,214,217],{},"然後輸入 ",[142,215,216],{},"node all.js","，這時候就來見證奇蹟的時候哩",[16,219,220],{},[48,221],{"alt":216,"src":222},"https:\u002F\u002Fi.imgur.com\u002FkQHaL4O.png",[16,224,225],{},"恭喜你已經入門 Node.js 哩~",[12,227,228],{"id":228},"補充",[16,230,231,232],{},"最後附上 Node.js 的 ",[62,233,236],{"href":234,"rel":235},"https:\u002F\u002Fgithub.com\u002Fnodejs\u002Fnode",[66],"GitHub",[16,238,239],{},"讓我們一起站在巨人的肩膀上來學習吧~",[241,242,243],"style",{},"html .default .shiki span {color: var(--shiki-default);background: var(--shiki-default-bg);font-style: var(--shiki-default-font-style);font-weight: var(--shiki-default-font-weight);text-decoration: var(--shiki-default-text-decoration);}html .shiki span {color: var(--shiki-default);background: var(--shiki-default-bg);font-style: var(--shiki-default-font-style);font-weight: var(--shiki-default-font-weight);text-decoration: var(--shiki-default-text-decoration);}",{"title":140,"searchDepth":245,"depth":245,"links":246},2,[247,248,253,254,255],{"id":14,"depth":245,"text":14},{"id":21,"depth":245,"text":22,"children":249},[250,252],{"id":40,"depth":251,"text":41},3,{"id":70,"depth":251,"text":71},{"id":99,"depth":245,"text":99},{"id":177,"depth":245,"text":178},{"id":228,"depth":245,"text":228},"Nodejs","2019-06-26 12:02:21","md","zh-Hant",{},true,"\u002Fnode.js\u002Fnode-js","2",{"title":6,"description":18},false,"全端勇士之路 Node.js\u002F全端勇士之路-Node-js-基礎學習-基礎篇",[22,268],"全端勇士之路 Node.js",null,"\u002Fnodejs\u002F20190626\u002F1885201810\u002F","6xqmLjyNtfFI7KN6nZtITZD7X_T2jCCTU8eyrlhxPIg",{"newer":273,"older":277},{"url":274,"title":275,"date":276},"\u002F